data.description: If you are looking for an affordable and spacious home on a quiet street, do not miss this one. 4 bed and 2 full baths, situated on one acre, with one bedroom conveniently located on the main level and two others upstairs. Large family room, eat-in kitchen and dining room, beautiful mountain views, large private backyard, great location, close to all amenities. Upstairs bedrooms are oversized. Home sold as is where is.
